---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="The B2B Tinkerers is a small group of senior B2B marketing strategists. We work quietly, think independently, and deliver real impact.">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero-inner">
    <div class="about-eyebrow">About us</div>
    <h1 class="about-h1">We're not an agency.<br>We're not a consultancy.<br>We're the person you<br>wish you'd hired sooner.</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MANIFESTO -->
<section class="about-manifesto">
  <div class="about-manifesto-inner">
    <div class="about-manifesto-left">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Who we are</div>
      <h2 class="about-h2">A small group of B2B marketing experts who've seen what works — and what doesn't.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-manifesto-right">
      <p>The B2B Tinkerers exists because most B2B companies spend too much on marketing that doesn't connect to business outcomes — and not enough on the thinking that would make it work.</p>
      <p>We're a deliberately small group of senior strategists with deep roots in B2B tech and industrial markets. We've led marketing teams, built GTM motions from scratch, repositioned brands, and sat in the rooms where budgets get cut and strategies get questioned.</p>
      <p>We don't subcontract. We don't scale by adding junior staff. When you work with us, you get the senior thinking — every time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="about-values">
  <div class="about-values-inner">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">How we think</div>
    <div class="about-values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-num">01</span>
        <div class="value-title">Strategy before tactics</div>
        <div class="value-body">Most marketing problems are strategy problems wearing a tactics costume. We fix the strategy first — then the tactics follow.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-num">02</span>
        <div class="value-title">Honest over comfortable</div>
        <div class="value-body">We'll tell you what we actually think, not what you want to hear. That's the only way the work produces real results.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-num">03</span>
        <div class="value-title">Business outcomes, not marketing metrics</div>
        <div class="value-body">Impressions and MQLs are not the goal. Revenue, pipeline, and market position are. We keep score the way the business does.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-num">04</span>
        <div class="value-title">Small on purpose</div>
        <div class="value-body">We don't want to be a 50-person agency. We want to do exceptional work for a small number of companies who take marketing seriously.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO WE WORK WITH -->
<section class="about-who">
  <div class="about-who-inner">
    <div class="about-who-left">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Who we work with</div>
      <h2 class="about-h2">B2B companies that are serious about growth — and honest about where they are.</h2>
      <p class="about-who-body">We work best with B2B tech and industrial companies between 10 and 200 people — typically at an inflection point. Entering a new market. Scaling past founder-led sales. Repositioning after a pivot. Building the marketing function for the first time.</p>
      <p class="about-who-body">What they have in common: a leadership team that knows marketing matters, and a willingness to do the work properly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-who-right">
      <div class="about-fit-card">
        <div class="fit-title">You're a good fit if:</div>
        <ul class="fit-list">
          <li>Your marketing spend isn't generating predictable pipeline</li>
          <li>Sales and marketing aren't pulling in the same direction</li>
          <li>You're entering a new market or repositioning</li>
          <li>You need senior marketing leadership without the full-time cost</li>
          <li>You want honest feedback, not flattery</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="about-notfit-card">
        <div class="fit-title">We're probably not the right fit if:</div>
        <ul class="fit-list">
          <li>You need someone to execute without strategic input</li>
          <li>You're looking for the cheapest option</li>
          <li>You want a large team with account managers and weekly status calls</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="about-cta">
  <div class="about-cta-inner">
    <h2 class="about-cta-h2">If this sounds like the kind of<br>thinking your business needs,<br>let's have a conversation.</h2>
    <p class="about-cta-sub">No pitch deck. No proposal on the first call. Just an honest conversation about where you are and whether we can help.</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:hello@theb2btinkerers.com">Get in touch →</a>
    <span class="about-cta-email">hello@theb2btinkerers.com</span>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
.about-hero{padding:calc(56px + clamp(60px,8vw,100px)) var(--pad) clamp(60px,8vw,96px);background:var(--forest);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.about-hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%,rgba(212,232,74,0.07) 0%,transparent 55%);pointer-events:none}
.about-hero-inner{max-width:780px}
.about-eyebrow{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lime);opacity:.65;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:20px}
.about-eyebrow::before{content:'';display:block;width:16px;height:1px;background:var(--lime)}
.about-h1{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,62px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:.97;color:var(--cream)}

.about-manifesto{padding:clamp(64px,9vw,108px) var(--pad);background:var(--cream)}
.about-manifesto-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(32px,6vw,80px);align-items:start}
@media(max-width:760px){.about-manifesto-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.section-eyebrow{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--forest);opacity:.4;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px}
.section-eyebrow::before{content:'';display:block;width:14px;height:1px;background:currentColor}
.about-h2{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,36px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.02;color:var(--forest)}
.about-manifesto-right p{font-size:clamp(14px,1.6vw,16px);line-height:1.85;color:rgba(26,26,26,.65);margin-bottom:20px}
.about-manifesto-right p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}

.about-values{padding:clamp(64px,9vw,108px) var(--pad);background:var(--forest)}
.about-values-inner{max-width:1080px}
.about-values .section-eyebrow{color:var(--cream);opacity:.22;margin-bottom:32px}
.about-values-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2px;margin-top:32px}
@media(max-width:900px){.about-values-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:480px){.about-values-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.value-card{background:var(--mid);padding:clamp(22px,3vw,34px) clamp(18px,2.5vw,26px)}
.value-card:nth-child(2){background:var(--lime)}
.value-num{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:38px;font-weight:800;color:var(--forest);opacity:.1;display:block;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px}
.value-card:nth-child(2) .value-num{opacity:.15}
.value-title{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(14px,1.8vw,17px);font-weight:700;color:var(--cream);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.2}
.value-card:nth-child(2) .value-title{color:var(--forest)}
.value-body{font-size:12px;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(245,240,232,.5)}
.value-card:nth-child(2) .value-body{color:rgba(28,74,58,.6)}

.about-who{padding:clamp(64px,9vw,108px) var(--pad);background:var(--linen)}
.about-who-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(32px,6vw,80px);align-items:start}
@media(max-width:760px){.about-who-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.about-who-body{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);line-height:1.85;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:16px}
.about-fit-card{background:var(--forest);padding:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);margin-bottom:2px}
.about-notfit-card{background:var(--cream);padding:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);border:1px solid rgba(28,74,58,.1)}
.fit-title{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:14px}
.about-fit-card .fit-title{color:var(--lime)}
.about-notfit-card .fit-title{color:var(--forest)}
.fit-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.fit-list li{font-size:13px;line-height:1.55;padding-left:16px;position:relative}
.fit-list li::before{content:'→';position:absolute;left:0;font-size:11px}
.about-fit-card .fit-list li{color:rgba(245,240,232,.65)}
.about-fit-card .fit-list li::before{color:var(--lime)}
.about-notfit-card .fit-list li{color:rgba(28,74,58,.55)}
.about-notfit-card .fit-list li::before{color:rgba(28,74,58,.3)}

.about-cta{padding:clamp(64px,9vw,108px) var(--pad);background:var(--forest)}
.about-cta-inner{max-width:640px}
.about-cta-h2{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,48px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:.97;color:var(--cream);margin-bottom:18px}
.about-cta-sub{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);line-height:1.8;color:rgba(245,240,232,.45);margin-bottom:32px;max-width:480px;display:block}
.btn-primary{background:var(--lime);color:var(--forest);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px 28px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;transition:opacity .15s;margin-bottom:16px}
.btn-primary:hover{opacity:.88}
.about-cta-email{display:block;font-size:13px;color:rgba(245,240,232,.3);margin-top:4px}
</style>
